column1: Little Goat Diner////Horrible house wine. The "spaghetti" breakfast contains literally four  spaghetti strings and a few runny eggs. The egg whites were raw. Some cheese
column2: four clams and some shredded crab. The only flavor was eggs and cheese.  The seafood was completely overwhelmed by the cheese and egg flavor. If I didn't see the clam n crab I would have thought I'm eating a cheese omelet. $15.
